data.title: Coupe de Luxembourg: Teams drawn for round of 16 in Luxembourg Cup
data.meta_description: In the last random draw for the first round of the football tournament Luxembourg Cup there were claims of rigging.
data.text:
On Monday, the teams were drawn for their allocation in the round of 16 in the Luxembourg Cup, as well as the first round of the Luxembourg Football Federation (FLF) Cup, the round of 16 for the Women's Cup, and the quarter finals for the Futsal Cup.

The Luxembourg Cup will have an exciting match between F91 Dudelange and Fola Esch. The draw has also revealed that Etzella Ettelbruck and Jeunesse Esch will play against each other and RM Hamm and Progrès Niederkorn will face each other.

The games will kick off on the weekend of 9 December.
